title: 'The Walking Dead' 6.03 Sneak Peeks: Make Sure You Get Back
text:
Comments Rick is walking alone and encounters a few walkers on the road while the group continues herding the walkers away. 
" The Walking Dead " has released sneak peeks for next week's episode following the airing of "JSS" on Sunday, October 18. In the upcoming outing, Rick and his group continue their mission to herd the quarry walkers away. Rick separates from the group and walks alone. On his way, he comes across a few walkers having a meal in the middle of the road as Glenn tells him a point of meeting via walkie-talkie. Meanwhile, Daryl is still leading the walkers, moving side by side with Abraham and Sasha who are in a car. Elsewhere, Michonne is hiding, waiting to slay the zombies coming to her way. "Thank You" airs October 25 at 9/8c on AMC. Official synopsis of the episode isn't available yet.
